head.title: Meetup RSVPs v2

item.comments: I'm sorry I can't make this one, but hopefuly next time.
I have know Richard for many years, I first met him when these events were just a dozen people or so at his home in Bedford...and it is great to see how this dream of his has grown!

I am so very sorry. I hope someone takes my stops; I see that there are three people in the waiting list. I live 140 miles away in Pittsfield-moving to Cambridge in June- and I was going, but now something came up. Have a great time!
Had a great time at last dance,looking forward to next one!!!

I am looking forward to having some fun, seeing Richard, familiar faces and new ones too. It will be 3 yrs to the month that I started attending Richard's dances including his house parties and the temple events. Let us all be positive!
Can't wait - sounds like loads of fun!!! Especially the part of being surrounded by happy people...definitely a plus.
I will be there with a friend. it will be our first time. iam sure we will have a lot of fun
May not be the best dancer, but I sure do enjoy it. Can't wait to get the party started.
bring someone else that is single
